data.description: Wow, Just Wow!! Amazing Home located on a Beautiful, Park like setting.  .82 acres backs up to Haddock Creek. Nature at it's finest!  House features 3 oversized Bedrooms, each w/dual closets. 2 Full Baths and 2 Half Baths. Primary Bedroom on main floor, Light, bright and Open Floorplan w/vaulted ceilings. Stately Fireplace boasts marble and custom mouldings. Large Kitchen has Island and 2 eating areas.  Impeccable craftsmanship. Amazing 3 car garage + insulated RV garage w/30 amp service. 1,700 sq ft of heated garage area,  so much space to store all of your "Big Toys".  Outside features a covered area for lawn equipment, Deck w/solar lighting, covered Breezeway w/sitting area and a pathway down to the creek.  This incredible House and Property are great for Entertaining and Gatherings.  Spacious "Dream Home" w/custom touches throughout.  Recent updates include, New Granite and Quartz, Sinks, Fixtures, Paint, Roof and Gutters. Main Amenities include Table Rock Lake access, Marina, 2 Golf Courses, Pools and Trails.
